text: The gentlemen that run Road Runner Taxi are very friendly and personable. They are reliable, and (considering the areas alternative) reasonably priced. I will definitely use them again.

name: Austin Stringer
text: Mr. Randy was excellent very friendly helped me when Uber and Lift wouldn’t may be a little more expensive but definitely worth it and a Christian can’t beat it.

name: Ronald Redd
text:
I called and set up a ride days in advance and was given a price based on the location of pick up and drop off. Then the driver went to a different location and we had to meet him there than he followed us to the spot he was suppose to pick us up. We got in the car, nice guy, but the driver started explaining he was the only person in the area. He kept going on about how there was no competition in the area, then doubled the original price.

We felt used and up charged for the driver's inability. I would not recommend this company or driver for any special fares, even if they told you it was not a problem.
